{"tid":2119394,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"黑店！大家小心 千期唔好幫襯","createTime":"2020-07-22T05:35:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-22T23:16:23.000Z","uid":305650,"like":4,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"080728ac8f6bb4a692e5dcd92e4f941a53bcc36b","tid":2119394,"uid":305650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T05:35:39.000Z","msg":"因爲疫情關係 所以怕左出去買送<br />\n係Facebook見到有間網店話可以代購買餸並且送貨上門<br />\n甘就試下買左$547.5，有菜有魚有肉有海鮮<br />\n點知惡夢就黎啦<br />\n我前一日order俾錢嘅時候remark左送貨時間係19：3后送貨<br />\n<br />\n但我當日16：30收到電話打黎話送貨到<br />\n我話屋企無人同埋我明明remark左19：30后先送貨。<br />\n跟住個位員工建議將啲餸挂係門口<br />\n有魚有肉有海鮮挂係門口2個幾鐘點都臭拉<br />\n我拒絕呢個做法，<br />\n跟住個位員工話打返公司聯絡<br />\n之後我無收到貨，whatapp問無人理<br />\n明明收錢個陣秒回，到追貨追退錢就keep住上綫但唔覆。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5eVe1sz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5eVe1sz.jpg&h=e85da994&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/17FFW0V.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F17FFW0V.jpg&h=1e7e9c73&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ttogvkV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FttogvkV.jpg&h=4931feb1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"59b8d60c451b7aa877c4c793948762599351de5b","tid":2119394,"uid":27719,"like":16,"dislike":2,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T05:37:24.000Z","msg":"開名啦仲同佢遮<br />\n遮你老母"},{"pid":"4733d7153db2e87936d0888197454de8d8b6e0ac","tid":2119394,"uid":64582,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T05:39:19.000Z","msg":"咁都唔開名人地彩你ON9 啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6867838d0fccc0a8fa909e22adf46c2918e27717","tid":2119394,"uid":74927,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T05:39:36.000Z","msg":"咪係 你POST出黎都想公審佢者<br />\n但係又要BLUR左名佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  咩玩法"},{"pid":"301fa01ba3fdbab276da788287f982cdf3cdf054","tid":2119394,"