citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T05:43:59.000Z","msg":"2日？等佢煮飯 餓死左啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22be26ce33abf2e5c3f32fe7870248bb15660445","tid":2119394,"uid":301923,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T05:44:06.000Z","msg":"炸爆佢電話啦<br />\n之前我考車肥佬揾學車王搶快期<br />\n我間中就問佢搶到未 <br />\n佢唔係話搶唔到 無人得閒搶<br />\n點知成個月都搶唔到<br />\n之後我叫佢退錢<br />\n點知佢online咗幾十次都唔應我<br />\n我火都黎<br />\n之後我直接炸爆佢電話<br />\n佢先死死氣應我機 <br />\n個陣我係咁迫佢即刻退錢<br />\n佢先嗱嗱聲幫我肯回水<br />\n然之後我揾第二個人搶 <br />\n佢第二日已經搶到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n對住啲無良奸商唔可以比任何喘息嘅空間佢<br />\n<br />\n利申：考到就甩P"},{"pid":"b5d9680c6e06e5cbdc09fe308a156fc6ec9cc3a5","tid":2119394,"uid":97775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"301fa01ba3fdbab276da788287f982cdf3cdf054","tid":2119394,"uid":24735,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T05:39:40.000Z","msg":"CHEN Q*** <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T05:47:53.000Z","msg":"9842<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23456d01ca86503cdb48d6a159f1e1ad49edba77","tid":2119394,"uid":27719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T06:08:28.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3a2ecce1d32e37815a12e71ba7d9ee617368290","tid":2119394,"uid":155253,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T06:10:35.000Z","msg":"咁撚怕死 買餸都要人送<br />\n抵你死啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"194fb37cc6e93a07c0306e8bca7af3086e6c83f9","tid":2119394,"uid":305650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d3a2ecce1d32e37815a12e71ba7d9ee61736829